      "summary": "A quantity number field component designed for flexible input and display of numeric quantities, with configurable minimum and maximum bounds. It provides interactive editing functionality including increment/decrement controls and input validation, as well as embedded and atom display variants for read-only contexts. Its primary purpose is to facilitate user input and display of quantity data within forms and interfaces, ensuring values stay within specified ranges.",
